== 製作 ==
2018年10月12日，據報導，[[連恩·尼遜|連恩·尼遜]]和{{le|凱特·華許|Kate Walsh (actress)}}將在驚悚片《倒數反擊》中分別飾演銀行搶劫犯湯姆·卡特（{{lang|en|Tom Carter}}）和他的愛人安妮（{{lang|en|Annie}}），該片由{{le|馬克·威廉斯 (製片人)|Mark Williams (filmmaker)|馬克·威廉斯}}執導，[[傑·寇特尼|傑·寇特尼]]與[[傑佛瑞·唐納文|傑佛瑞·唐納文]]也有望出演。威廉斯也和梅爾斯·內斯特爾（{{lang|en|Myles Nestel}}）、泰·鄧肯（{{lang|en|Tai Duncan}}）、克雷格·查普曼（{{lang|en|Craig Chapman}}）共同擔任監製<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jr |first1=Mike Fleming |title=Liam Neeson, Kate Walsh To Star In ‘Honest Thief’ |url=https://deadline.com/2018/10/liam-neeson-kate-walsh-honest-thief-movie-mark-williams-1202481564/ |accessdate=2018-10-12 |work=Deadline |date=2018-10-12 |archive-date=2018-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012201230/https://deadline.com/2018/10/liam-neeson-kate-walsh-honest-thief-movie-mark-williams-1202481564/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月，[[安東尼·拉莫斯|安東尼·拉莫斯]]和[[羅伯特·派屈克|羅伯特·派屈克]]相繼加入演出陣容，[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]也於同月5日開始進行<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/news/hamilton-star-anthony-ramos-liam-neeson-honest-thief-1203016067/|title=‘Hamilton’ Star Anthony Ramos Joins Liam Neeson’s ‘Honest Thief’ (EXCLUSIVE)|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=Variety|date=2018-11-01|accessdate=2020-10-06|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820201418/https://variety.com/2018/film/news/hamilton-star-anthony-ramos-liam-neeson-honest-thief-1203016067/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2018/11/robert-patrick-liam-neeson-kate-walsh-honest-thief-movie-cast-1202508975/|title=Robert Patrick In Talks To Board Liam Neeson-Kate Walsh Action-Thriller ‘Honest Thief’|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=Deadline|date=2018-11-26|accessdate=2020-10-06|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920163337/https://deadline.com/2018/11/robert-patrick-liam-neeson-kate-walsh-honest-thief-movie-cast-1202508975/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片大多在[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]][[波士頓|波士頓]]和[[伍斯特_(马萨诸塞州)|伍斯特]]及其周圍地區拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wickedlocal.com/entertainmentlife/2