== 發行 ==
《倒數反擊》由[[開路影業|開路影業]]定於2020年10月16日美國上映。臺灣先於2020年10月8日上映，由[[威視電影|威視電影]]發行<ref name="@movies" />。

2020年1月，{{le|湯姆·奧滕伯格|Tom Ortenberg|Briarcliff Entertainment}}取得該片的美國發行權，並將其定於2020年9月4日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/honest-thief-liam-neeson-briarcliff-entertainment-distribution-deal-1202838110/|title=Briarcliff Entertainment Acquires U.S. Rights To ‘Honest Thief;’ Action Thriller Stars Liam Neeson & Kate Walsh|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2020-01-22|accessdate=2020-01-22|archive-date=2020-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200123160120/https://deadline.com/2020/01/honest-thief-liam-neeson-briarcliff-entertainment-distribution-deal-1202838110/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；之後改為2020年10月9日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/honest-thief-trailer-liam-neeson-movie/|title=Liam Neeson Blows Shit Up in Exclusive Trailer for Crime Thriller ‘Honest Thief’|website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]]|first=Adam|last=Chitwood|date=2020-07-30|accessdate=2020-07-30|archive-date=2020-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200731121158/https://collider.com/honest-thief-trailer-liam-neeson-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年6月，開路影業將與Briarcliff共同發行該片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/open-road-relaunches-liam-neesons-honest-thief-thriller-1299650|title=Open Road Relaunches With Liam Neeson's 'Honest Thief' Thriller|website=The Hollywood Reporter|first=Etan|last=Vlessing|date=2020-06-22|accessdate=2020-07-30|archive-date=2020-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200827234856/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/open-road-relaunches-liam-neesons-honest-thief-thriller-1299650|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的影響，該片暫時撤下檔期後，美國上映日又重新改檔為2020年10月16日<ref>{{cite web |url= https://deadline.com/2020/09/liam-neeson-honest-thief-release-date-change-october-open-road-1234582450/ |title= Open Road’s Liam Neeson Action-Thriller ‘Honest Thief’ Going Wide This Fall, A Week Later |website= Deadline Hollywood |first= Anthony |last= D'Alessandro |date= 2020-09-22 |accessdate= 2020-09-22 |archive-date= 2020-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200924090325/https://deadline.com/2020/09/liam-neeson-honest-thief-release-date-change-october-open-road-1234582450/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

